    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know, i'm just really worried about the cost of the clinic and it's late here. i've read a lot about medical grade honey being used for skin healing though. if i clean it really well first, wouldn't that be enough to stop it from getting infected? i really don't want to go to the ER if i can avoid it.",
